.TH "__genphy_config_aneg" 9 "__genphy_config_aneg" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
__genphy_config_aneg \- restart auto-negotiation or write BMCR
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" __genphy_config_aneg
.BI "(struct phy_device *phydev "  ","
.BI "bool changed "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "phydev" 12
target phy_device struct
.IP "changed" 12
whether autoneg is requested
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If auto-negotiation is enabled, we configure the
advertising, and then restart auto-negotiation.  If it is not
enabled, then we write the BMCR.
